**About the Artist**

I am 26 years old and I live in Brazil, specifically in Minas Gerais.
My passion for art runs in my family. My grandfather and father were both artists, and now I am too. Despite not having formal art education, it always felt natural to me. I grew up watching my father and admiring my grandfather's paintings on our walls. It gave me a clear sense of my path. After high school, I tried studying law and then administration, but something was missing.

Even before finishing college, I was freelancing in tattooing, photography, and illustration. In 2021, I had my first solo exhibition in Brasilia. The experience was incredible.
